    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/a12cd668508fab46917674c29716cc74.poster.avif?t=1745506255\" width=614 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/a12cd668508fab46917674c29716cc74.webm?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/a12cd668508fab46917674c29716cc74.mp4?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>《The Fabulous Fear Machine》</i>是由<i>《Do Not Feed the Monkeys》</i>的作者打造的一款带有通俗恐怖风格的叙事类策略游戏。你刚成为恐怖机器的新主人，现在必须通过打出传奇卡牌来散播恐惧并扩大自己影响力：也就是传播那些潜伏在心灵黑暗角落的恐怖故事、都市传说以及阴谋论。 <br><br>要想让你的传奇不断成长，你需要派遣特工前往地图上的新地点，收获并管理资源，决定如何处理模拟中的事件，并监视敌人的行动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/99ac9de1dcd8ac2ef0db5f2f91cff2cc.poster.avif?t=1745506255\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/99ac9de1dcd8ac2ef0db5f2f91cff2cc.webm?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/99ac9de1dcd8ac2ef0db5f2f91cff2cc.mp4?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你内心深处的渴望是什么？权力，财富，荣耀？拥有了<i>《The Fabulous Fear Machine》</i>，你曾经所梦想的一切都将触手可及。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/2eb8089796b6849961366179408d78d8.poster.avif?t=1745506255\" width=614 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/2eb8089796b6849961366179408d78d8.webm?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/2eb8089796b6849961366179408d78d8.mp4?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>选择你的毒物。</strong>从黑妖犬这样的神秘生物，到血腥玛丽之类的都市传奇，再到诸如蜥蜴人等的阴谋论——超过80个传奇供你选择，为你造访的每座城市量身打造恐怖风格。<br><br><strong>恐怖现已进化。</strong>在肥沃的土地上散播恐怖的种子。观看并聆听媒体对你那些传奇故事的反应。通过不断地添油加醋，看着它们变得更加强大、更加蛊惑人心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/4da96841b694cf9495bdb4a5de055197.poster.avif?t=1745506255\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/4da96841b694cf9495bdb4a5de055197.webm?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/4da96841b694cf9495bdb4a5de055197.mp4?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>以恰当的方式完成任务。</strong>你的优势在于制定策略；将脏活累活都交给你的特工。派他们去探索新的地点，渗透进敌人内部，一路上做出有趣的抉择。 <br><br><strong>相等和相反的反应。</strong>竞争对手和善良的力量都试图为了各自的目的消除恐怖机器的影响力。相应地做出计划，不然你可能会发现自己的传奇故事被扭曲成了励志故事、吉祥物，或者其他甜蜜的陈词滥调。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/da28bb2b598c52ebc96b9b00cf9b1b10.poster.avif?t=1745506255\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/da28bb2b598c52ebc96b9b00cf9b1b10.webm?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1540350/extras/da28bb2b598c52ebc96b9b00cf9b1b10.mp4?t=1745506255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>如时光般古老的故事。</strong>讲述在世界不同地区行动的几名主人的故事。一路走来，探索恐怖机器、它的敌人以及帮助你的那些特工的历史。<br><br><i>由 AMC Games 和 SHUDDER 出品。本游戏的早期开发由 Red.es 和 FEDER（欧洲地区开发基金）支持。</i>",
